  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Wat</b> is a common male name in Westeros. It may refer to:\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Characters\">Characters</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wat&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Characters\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>Wat, the real name of the <a href=\"/index.php/Blue_Bard\" title=\"Blue Bard\">Blue Bard</a>, a singer.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Wat_(Night%27s_Watch)\" title=\"Wat (Night&#39;s Watch)\">Wat</a>, a member of the Night's Watch.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Wat_(Standfast)\" title=\"Wat (Standfast)\">Wat</a>, a farmer in service to House Osgrey.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Wat_(orphan)\" title=\"Wat (orphan)\">Wat</a>, an orphan boy.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Wat_(sailor)\" title=\"Wat (sailor)\">Wat</a>, a member of the crew of the <i>Brazen Monkey</i>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Wat_Barleycorn\" title=\"Wat Barleycorn\">Wat Barleycorn</a>, a farmer in service to House Osgrey.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Wat_the_Hewer\" title=\"Wat the Hewer\">Wat the Hewer</a>, a member of the Poor Fellows during the Faith Militant uprising.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Wat_the_Tanner\" title=\"Wat the Tanner\">Wat the Tanner</a>, a tanner during the Dance of the Dragons.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Wet_Wat\" title=\"Wet Wat\">Wet Wat</a>, a farmer in service to House Osgrey, brother of Wat Barleycorn.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Whitesmile_Wat\" title=\"Whitesmile Wat\">Whitesmile Wat</a>, a singer in service to House Lannister.</li></ul>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Wat_(ranger)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Wat (ranger)\">Wat</a>, a character created for the video game <i>Game of Thrones</i>.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Places\">Places</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wat&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Places\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Wat%27s_Wood\" title=\"Wat&#39;s Wood\">Wat's Wood</a> is the forest located on <a href=\"/index.php/House_Osgrey\" title=\"House Osgrey\">House Osgrey</a> lands.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wat&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: See also\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Wate\" title=\"Wate\">Wate</a>, a guardsmen in service to House Targaryen.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Watt_of_Long_Lake\" title=\"Watt of Long Lake\">Watt of Long Lake</a>, a member of the Night's Watch.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Watty\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Watty\">Watty</a>, a miller.</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404082113\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.005 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.006 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 11/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 16/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:8877-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404082113 and revi